                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7246" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0727</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7564 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">檀有庆创办香檀别院：机会导向还是资源导向?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tan Youqing founded Xiangtan Bieyuan:opportunity-oriented or resource-oriented?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田秀华，孔恒洋，周雨琴，李永发</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">池州香檀别院硒产品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业；机会导向；资源导向；资源整合；创业能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">entrepreneurship,opportunity-oriented,resource-oriented, resource integration, entrepreneurial ability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">檀有庆是石台县牯牛降解放后当兵第一人，学习汽车修理，2001年转业南京后一直思考：怎样才能让贫穷的乡亲们真正过上好生活？2003年法国雷诺车作为公务用车不适应南京气候，高温会熄火。檀有庆感知到维修雷诺车是一个好的创业机会，便辞了铁饭碗，创办修理厂。随着会员增多，檀有庆想着给会员们配送家乡有机瓜果蔬菜。配送的蔬菜往往存在剩余，为了避免浪费，同时发现南京吃高品质有机蔬菜有一定市场，于是，创立有机素食馆。为了更好地带动家乡经济，喝着牯牛降山泉水长大的檀有庆看到家乡富硒山泉水蕴含的商机。于是， 2016年，檀有庆建立檀泉水厂。不过品牌桶装水竞争日益激烈，仅2021年，石台县新增十几个水厂。本案例聚焦创业研究的核心问题：创业机会的识别与利用，帮助学习者理解创业机会导向、资源导向与初心导向，掌握资源获取与整合策略。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tan Youqing was the first person to serve in the army after the release of Gu Niujiang in Shitai County. He studied auto repair. After moving to Nanjing in 2001, he has been thinking: How to make the poor villagers truly live a good life? In 2003, the French Renault car was not suitable for the Nanjing climate as an official car, and the high temperature would stall. Tan Youqing felt that repairing Renault cars was a good entrepreneurial opportunity, so he quit his job and started a repair shop.  As the number of members increased, Tan Youqing wanted to deliver organic fruits and vegetables to members from his hometown. There is often a surplus of vegetables delivered. In order to avoid waste, he found that there is a certain market for high-quality organic vegetables in Nanjing, so he set up an organic vegetarian restaurant. In order to better drive the economy of his hometown, Tan Youqing, who grew up drinking the spring water of Gu Niujiang, saw the business opportunities contained in the spring water rich in selenium in his hometown. Therefore, in 2016, Tan Youqing established Tanquan water plant. However, the competition for brand bottled water is increasingly fierce. In 2021 alone, more than a dozen water plants will be added in Shitai County. This case focuses on the core issue of entrepreneurship research: the identification and utilization of entrepreneurial opportunities, helping learners to understand entrepreneurial opportunity orientation, resource orientation and original intention orientation, and master resource acquisition and integration strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会识别能力；资源管理能力；创业机会；创业资源；机会识别与资源获取；机会资源一体化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
